======================================
  NEXUS: NEXT Utility for Simulation
======================================

This is a Geant4-based application to study the possibilities offered 
by a High Pressure Xenon gas TPC in the search for the neutrinoless 
double beta decay (bb0nu).

NEXT stands for "Neutrino Experiment with a Xenon TPC".

